---
title: Tex-Mex Pulled Pork Loaded Fries with Cheddar, Charred Corn Salsa & Sour Cream
description: We have a question. Why have everything separate on the plate when you could have it all together? For example,
may we present this glowing plate of pulled pork in an enchilada sauce on top of golden fries, all held together by
strings of gooey Cheddar cheese. We’ll look the other way when you lick the plate.
